snippet.title: Thief Town - PC Release Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY Thief Town on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/331220

Thief Town is a multiplayer-only stealth action game set in a pixel-perfect rendition of the Wild West. Lurk in the crowd, emulate non-player characters, and achieve backstabbing victory.

Check out the Glass Knuckle website for our other games:
http://www.glassknuckle.com

Glass Knuckle Games on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/GlassKnuckleGames

Sign up for the Glass Knuckle Newsletter for development updates and more!
